<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1901-09-14T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1901-09-14T00:00:00-05:00" n="42" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d42">
                        <head><hi rend="italic">President <persName type="from">Campos
                                    Sables</persName> to the <gloss type="to">Vice-President of the
                                    United States</gloss>.</hi></head>
                        <opener><seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg></opener>
                        <opener><dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Rio de
                                        Janeiro</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1901-09-14"><hi rend="italic">September 14,
                                    1901</hi></date>.</dateline></opener>
                        <p>I desire to extend to your excellency expression of my profound sorrow at
                            the loss which the American nation has just suffered in the death of its
                            First Magistrate.</p>
                        <closer><signed><hi rend="smallcaps">M. Ferraz de Campos
                                    Salles</hi>,<lb/><hi rend="italic">President of the United
                                    States of Brazil.</hi></signed></closer>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>